support of the other democratic states of Europe and the solidarity of
international conferences of free countries so that your freedom of decision
and action can be fulfilled.'
He said Lithuania's desire to join the European Community eventually was
legitimate but added: 'Let us not speed things up faster than is
appropriate. Let us plan the (intervening) time.'
