<TEXT>
THE NUCPS Civil Service union reacted angrily yesterday to the news that
Astra Training Services, which took over the bulk of the 60 skill centres
privatised in 1990, had announced to staff a further three rounds of
closures and redundancies.
Rochdale, Somerset and Redmouth centres are to close, and other redundancies
