FT  15 MAY 92 / UK Company News: 22% downturn at Tomkinsons
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In another difficult interim period, Tomkinsons, the floor coverings group,
limited its drop in sales to just over 4 per cent, but saw pre-tax profit
fall by 22 per cent.
