Desmond Fitzgerald, chief executive of Mathews, Mulcahy &amp; Sutherland, md of
Marsh &amp; McLennan Inc and a member of the executive committee of Bowring
Marsh &amp; McLennan Ltd, has been appointed to the board of MARSH &amp; McLENNAN
EUROPE.
